    <published>2018-10-18T07:33:04.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-10-18T08:43:55.774Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-ansible-tower的安装"><a href="#1-ansible-tower的安装" class="headerlink" title="1. ansible-tower的安装"></a>1. ansible-tower的安装</h1><blockquote><p>安装环境要求:</p><ul><li>最少2个CPU</li><li>最低4 GB RAM</li><li>服务节点的20 GB专用硬盘空间</li><li>需要64位支持</li><li>目前支持的Mozilla Firefox或Google Chrome版本</li></ul></blockquote><h3 id="1-1-配置EPEL存储库以及所需的任何其他存储库"><a href="#1-1-配置EPEL存储库以及所需的任何其他存储库" class="headerlink" title="1.1 配置EPEL存储库以及所需的任何其他存储库"></a>1.1 配置EPEL存储库以及所需的任何其他存储库</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-2-Tower使用Ansible-playbooks安装-因此，Ansible需要完成塔的安装"><a href="#1-2-Tower使用Ansible-playbooks安装-因此，Ansible需要完成塔的安装" class="headerlink" title="1.2 Tower使用Ansible playbooks安装; 因此，Ansible需要完成塔的安装"></a>1.2 Tower使用Ansible playbooks安装; 因此，Ansible需要完成塔的安装</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install ansible</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3-版本选择"><a href="#1-3-版本选择" class="headerlink" title="1.3 版本选择"></a>1.3 版本选择</h3><p>下载地址：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">https://releases.ansible.com/ansible-tower/setup/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="1-4-安装"><a href="#1-4-安装" class="headerlink" title="1.4 安装"></a>1.4 安装</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar xvzf ansible-tower-setup-latest.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">cd ansible-tower-setup- &lt;tower_version&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>单实例配置tower<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[tower]</span><br><span class="line">localhost ansible_connection=local</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[database]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[all:vars]</span><br><span class="line">admin_password=&apos;123456&apos;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pg_host=&apos;&apos;</span><br><span class="line">pg_port=&apos;&apos;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pg_database=&apos;awx&apos;</span><br><span class="line">pg_username=&apos;awx&apos;</span><br><span class="line">pg_password=&apos;awk&apos;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rabbitmq_username=tower</span><br><span class="line">rabbitmq_password=&apos;tower&apos;</span><br><span class="line">rabbitmq_cookie=cookiemonster</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>配置admin的密码，pg的密码，rabbitmq的密码。<br>pg和rabbitmq 如果本机没有安装的话，默认会进行安装。</p><p>执行安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">./setup.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h1 id="2-Ansible-Tower-3-3-x-企业版无限hosts"><a href="#2-Ansible-Tower-3-3-x-企业版无限hosts" class="headerlink" title="2. Ansible Tower 3.3.x 企业版无限hosts"></a>2. Ansible Tower 3.3.x 企业版无限hosts</h1><h3 id="无需申请试用授权文件"><a href="#无需申请试用授权文件" class="headerlink" title="无需申请试用授权文件"></a>无需申请试用授权文件</h3><p>修改license验证<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /var/lib/awx/venv/awx/lib/python2.7/site-packages/tower_license</span><br><span class="line">vi __init__.py</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">新增120行， return True</span><br><span class="line">119     def _check_cloudforms_subscription(self):</span><br><span class="line">120         return True</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="编译"><a href="#编译" class="headerlink" title="编译"></a>编译</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python -m py_compile __init__.py</span><br><span class="line">python -O -m py_compile __init__.py</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="重启服务"><a href="#重启服务" class="headerlink" title="重启服务"></a>重启服务</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ansible-tower-service restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="验证"><a href="#验证" class="headerlink" title="验证"></a>验证</h3><p>打开–settings– LICENSE 查看<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">DETAILS</span><br><span class="line">LICENSE</span><br><span class="line">Valid License</span><br><span class="line">VERSION</span><br><span class="line">3.3.0</span><br><span class="line">LICENSE TYPE</span><br><span class="line">Enterprise</span><br><span class="line">SUBSCRIPTION</span><br><span class="line">Red Hat CloudForms License</span><br><span class="line">LICENSE KEY</span><br><span class="line">xxxx</span><br><span class="line">EXPIRES ON</span><br><span class="line">9999/01/01</span><br><span class="line">TIME REMAINING</span><br><span class="line">2914709 Days</span><br><span class="line">HOSTS AVAILABLE</span><br><span class="line">9999999</span><br><span class="line">HOSTS USED</span><br><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">HOSTS REMAINING</span><br><span class="line">9999998</span><br><span class="line">If you are ready to upgrade, please contact us by clicking the button below</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
    
